blog.name: autonomy1
blog.title: Peter Percival-AUTONOMY
blog.description: Shades, nuances, scraps of existence......looking directly at an object can sometimes be a meaningless, even a destructive use of time…in society we are trained to look at things quickly, process that information and move on to another view…so much information and meaning can be lost in the action of moving on….by changing the expected angle of view, or re-arranging elements of an image one can derive another meaning from it, and if not an absolute meaning an abstract one which makes us look once again…that is all one can ask for, another look…(©) Pete Percival - 2013 All Rights Reserved. Reproduction of any kind is illegal.

summary:
This is my beautiful cannibalistic slime boi, Dāku Yonaga!

 Time taken: About 3 days, finished at 1 am on June 23, 2018

...
caption:
This is my beautiful cannibalistic slime boi, Dāku Yonaga!

Time taken: About 3 days, finished at 1 am on June 23, 2018

Media: iPad Pro, Procreate App, iPencil

I love space and slimes, so I tried combining the two and made a fabulous monster who I’m very proud of!

I started this before I decided he wears clothes so I’ll draw him with that later I guess lol, he’s Japanese and actually sort of a villain OC for Boku No Hero Academia, but he’s also his own thing besides being an insert for that too, I’m still working on more background details.

So far he’s a cannibal/carnivorous slime monster with a space-like appearance that can turn his arms into large mouth-like limbs along with being able to stretch them extremely far. The spikes are made of hardened slime substance that’s sharp and pointed into spikes that randomly stick out of his arms as well as form a mouth shape on his face in his normal form, however, all the spikes will form into a mouth shape on one or both arms rather than his face when in predatory mode.
He usually eats other slimes, but he’ll also eat basically anything else.
He can also put creatures in suspended animation within his body through absorption not through the mouth(s) which are specifically for eating and attacking.
He uses his mesmerizing space-like appearance to lure in victims.
His favorite non-living thing to eat is actually honey, which he ironically prefers over honey-slimes as to who he claims “don’t taste as good or sweet as actual honey, and are more plain” so he will leave honey slimes alone for the most part unless they’re annoying or the only option. He also prefers sweet, spicy, and savory slimes over bitter, bland, and sour slimes.

That’s all I got for him so far I hope y’all like him!!!
He’s available for ask at @interstellactic-oc-ask
